you to compute that constant that you didn't

59
00:03:41.890 --> 00:03:42.890
know.

60
00:03:42.890 --> 00:03:47.689
That it was $2.50, and it would compute the relationship
between the fare and and the distance and

61
00:03:47.689 --> 00:03:49.232
the fare and the time.

62
00:03:49.232 --> 00:03:49.249
That is regression.

